713
01:02:07,904 --> 01:02:12,464
Fortunately, I brought my desk and chair
from our old house.

714
01:02:13,185 --> 01:02:14,745
They might be old,

715
01:02:15,665 --> 01:02:17,024
but I really like them.

716
01:02:19,145 --> 01:02:20,984
It's my favorite desk.

717
01:02:21,545 --> 01:02:23,585
