01:03:39,904 --> 01:03:41,464
I shouldn't have bought it.

736
01:03:43,065 --> 01:03:44,864
She complained it was expensive.

737
01:03:44,944 --> 01:03:46,024
What's the matter?

738
01:03:47,345 --> 01:03:48,904
What else did he write?

739
01:03:52,065 --> 01:03:55,705
He wrote that you complained
it was expensive.

740
01:04:12,024 --> 01:04:15,825
I don't need something
this new and expensive.

741
01:04:15,904 --> 01:04:17,864
You should have saved the money.

742
01:04:29,665 --> 01:04:31,345
I didn't know what to do.

743
01:04:31,864 --> 01:04:34,384
I didn't mean to be insensitive.

744
01:04:37,544 --> 01:04:40,305
I should have told him how good it felt

745
01:04:41,265 --> 01:04:43,544
that he had thought of me.

746
01:04:44,544 --> 01:04:48,024
I should have at least said thank you.

747
01:04:50,145 --> 01:04:52,024
But I didn't say that.

748
01:04:53,864 --> 01:04:56,665
Nut wanted you to have a good phone,

749
01:04:57,665 --> 01:05:01,265
while you wanted him
to keep the money for himself.

750
01:05:02,024 --> 01:05:04,145
You both had different ways

751
01:05:04,225 --> 01:05:05,904
of showing good intentions.

752
01:05:06,504 --> 01:05:08,944
