01:05:18,984 --> 01:05:20,705
What else did he write?

755
01:05:21,825 --> 01:05:23,065
There's more.

756
01:05:24,864 --> 01:05:26,984
I've already bought
everything for the house,

757
01:05:27,544 --> 01:05:29,504
