to stay home with you,

767
01:06:06,825 --> 01:06:09,145
Nut is always trying to take care of you.

768
01:06:14,145 --> 01:06:15,785
I'm very lucky.

769
01:06:17,745 --> 01:06:19,424
He might be stubborn at times,

770
01:06:20,904 --> 01:06:22,825
