the harsh reality.

774
01:06:49,464 --> 01:06:50,665
The reality

775
01:06:51,825 --> 01:06:54,065
that Nut hardly ever writes about her.

776
01:06:55,745 --> 01:06:57,185
When he writes about her,

777
01:06:58,745 --> 01:07:00,745
