786
01:07:43,745 --> 01:07:45,065
That's hard to say.

787
01:07:45,544 --> 01:07:49,984
There's more to what she did
than I can get from the script.

788
01:07:51,904 --> 01:07:55,504
It's not easy to tell
without scratching the surface.

